summary: When Ultimate Spider-man (the show) started, I watched some of it but didn’t stick because it wasn’t all that great.  Anyway now...
body:
When Ultimate Spider-man (the show) started, I watched some of it but didn’t stick because it wasn’t all that great.

Anyway now I’m watching the episode where Loki switches bodies with Peter, and it’s great? Like seriously it’s awesome, I didn’t expect that. The guy who plays Loki does a great Peter and Peter getting thrown around as Loki is amazing; but the really cool thing is at the end of the first part, once the Avengers figure out Loki and Peter switched bodies Loki switches them back so the Avengers are now going after Peter and Loki is pretending to be Peter. It’s awesome.

And like, I freaking hate body-swap plots; they’ve scared me since I was a child, but this one is so funny

summary:
Peter B. Parker, standing on a street corner, in full costume, playing a guitar and singing: 
Spider-Man, Spider-Man, 
He needs...
body:
Peter B. Parker, standing on a street corner, in full costume, playing a guitar and singing:


Spider-Man, Spider-Man,

He needs a new picture cam!

Is he paid for any fight?

Not for all his work tonight!


Woah, here comes the Bankrupt-Man!

Does he work? All night and day!

But he never gets any pay!

Tony Stark is a stingy guy!

Never lets one mistake fly!

Look out, here comes broke Spider-Man!


In the chill of night,

At the scene of a crime,

He comes in ripped-up tights,

Can’t afford to spend a dime!


Spider-Man, Spider-Man,

No new equipment, Spider-Man!

Is he hungry? All the time!

He can’t afford to buy a lime!


To him, life is a great big hang-up!

Whenever he gets banged-up!

Come on, please help out Spider-Man!

Origin: Was raised in a circus with her older brother Peter Parker. They were the main atraction...
body:
Spidersona

Name: Katie Parker

Origin: Was raised in a circus with her older brother Peter Parker. They were the main atraction till a cult I kidnapped both her and Peter. The cult had a demon spider bite both of them then tried to sacrifice them. Then Katie broke free then ran to the cops, half the cult escaped the other half was arrested. Katie and Peter were taken to a hospital, but Peter died at midnight. Katie lives with her aunt and uncle. Now she fights monsters, demons, and serial killers while looking for the rest of the cult who killed her brother.

This is basically a marvel/creepypasta crossover
